@SquadIA_HostAddress = http://localhost:5103

### Health-like check via dashboard
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/dashboard
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar nova análise
POST {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/analisar
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "nomeSquad": "Payments Squad",
  "leadTimeMedio": 70,
  "throughput": 8,
  "bugs": 20,
  "bloqueios": 6
}

###

### Listar histórico paginado
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/historico?pagina=1&tamanhoPagina=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Filtrar histórico por squad
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/historico?nomeSquad=Payments&pagina=1&tamanhoPagina=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Filtrar histórico por período
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/historico?dataInicial=2026-04-01&dataFinal=2026-04-30
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar histórico por ID
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/historico/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Dashboard com filtro por squad
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/dashboard?nomeSquad=Payments
Accept: application/json

###

### Exportar CSV
GET {{SquadIA_HostAddress}}/api/Squad/exportar?nomeSquad=Payments
Accept: text/csv